    "group_visual_density_select": "Control how much ibibonwa imfashanyo umunyeshure muri iki group akira. 'High' adds vyinshi ifoto na ishusho.",
    "group_tts_speed_select": "Adjust inyandiko-ku-speech playback umuvuduko. Slower speeds imfashanyo struggling readers follow along.",
